      "span_text": "Erythrocytes were depleted by treatment with lysis buffer, containing of NH 4 Cl (8.3 g/l) and KHCO (1 g/l) on ice, for 5 min and washed twice immediately with RPMI medium supplemented with 10% fetal calf serum."
